    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi dei eterni, anno ab incarnatione eius
                        millesimo centesimo vigesimo quinto, tertiodecimo kalendas novembris,
                        indictione quarta. (…) <persName>Rolandus</persName> filius quondam
                            <persName>Sismundi</persName> et <persName><name ref="Aza"
                            >Atha</name></persName> iugalis filia quondam *** et
                            <persName>Ermanno</persName> atque <persName>Stranbo</persName> germanii
                        filii eiusdem Rolandi et <persName><name ref="Wizo"
                            >Guithone</name></persName> qd. <persName><name ref="Massaiolus"
                                >Massaioli</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Winigildus"
                                >Guineldo</name></persName> f. eius et <persName><name
                                ref="Cacciatus">Cacciato</name></persName> atque <persName><name
                                ref="Moricone">Moricone</name></persName> gg. qd. <persName><name
                                ref="Bernardus">Bernardi</name></persName>
                        <ref>ricevono da</ref>
                        <persName key="#Priors"><name ref="Savinus">Savinus</name></persName> prior
                            <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs> et <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/3205">Sancti
                            Georgii</orgName> huius Lucane civitatis … <rs key="#Meritum/launechild"
                            >meritum anulum aureum;</rs>
                        <ref>perciò promettono di</ref> litem nec intentionem neque aliquam
                        molestiam mittere neque facere … de una petia de terra que est in loco
                            <placeName ref="#places/3208"
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Forests #Wine #Hay/fodder"
                            >Cerbaria</placeName>, que est <rs key="#Forests">bossco et <geogName
                                ref="#estates/3201"
                                key="#Landed_possessions #Forests #Wine #Hay/fodder"
                                >silva</geogName></rs> atque <rs key="#Wine">vinea</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder">prato</rs> atque <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terra
                            culta et inculta</rs> atque agresta una cum omnibus edificiis que sunt
                        per circuitum ecclesie <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3204">Sancti
                            Nazari</orgName>, omnia insimul amembrata cuius fines ita sunt: ab uno
                        videlicet capite sicut crux est que vocatur Pisciatina, usque ad crucem
                        aliam sicut strada percurrit, et ex uno latere a suprascripta cruce
                        Pisciatina usque ad Valle de Fatuchaca et usque ad aquam de Palude, ex alio
                        latere sicut predicta crux alia esse videtur usque ad <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >rivum</rs> qui dicitur Ganbaraio et sicut ipse rivus percurrit usque ad
                        aqua de palude. <ref>Pena</ref>: pena argenti optimi libras viginti. Actum
                        intus <rs key="#Castle">castrum</rs> de <placeName key="#Castle"
                            ref="#places/3211">Via Venaria</placeName>. (…) <ref>(autografo)</ref>
                        (S) <rs key="#Judge">Iudicis</rs> est signum <persName key="#Judge"><name
                                ref="Richardus">Ricardi</name></persName> pollice pictum. Signa
                        manuum <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Wilielmus"
                            >Guililemi</name></persName> qd. <persName><name ref="Concettus"
                                >Conceti</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Gallus">Gallete</name></persName> qd. <persName><name
                                ref="Gherardus">Gerardi</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Ciabactellus">Ciabactelli</name></persName>
                        qd. <persName><name ref="Walandus">Gualandi</name></persName> rogatorum <rs
                            key="#Witness">testium</rs>. Signa manuum <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Ildebrandus">Ildebrandi</name></persName> f. <persName><name
                                ref="Bernardus">Bernardi</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Guiscardus">Guiscardi</name></persName> f.
                                <persName><name ref="Brunellus">Brunelli</name></persName> rogatorum
                        testium. <ref>Scrive</ref>
                        <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Lanfrancus"
                            >Lanfrancus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> domni regis. </ab>
